https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/docker.html#docker-configuration-methods

---------------------------------
Confiuration
---------------------------------

- config files are loaded from '/usr/share/elasticsearch/config/'
- override files using bind mounts
- override single variables using docker environment variables

Depending on the orchestration platform, properties
have to be uppercase with '_' insteat of '.'
- bootstrap.memory_lock=true
- ES_SETTING_BOOTSTRAP_MEMORY__LOCK=true

---------------------------------
Password file
---------------------------------
bind-mount the bootstrap password file

-e ELASTIC_PASSWORD_FILE=/run/secrets/bootstrapPassword.txt



